27/08/2010
TIRANA, Albania -- Police in the northern city of Shkodra busted a criminal gang Thursday (August 26th) suspected of weapons trafficking, drug smuggling and illegal vehicle imports. Seven people active in Shkodra, Lezha and Durres were arrested. Police say they also seized 1kg of heroin, 4kg of marijuana, guns, ammunition, stolen cars, and tools for forging documents and weighing drugs. (News 24, Balkan Web, Lajmifundit, Telegrafi - 26/08/10)
